      "text": "The Democrat DHS Shutdown has Consequences for American Citizens and Hardworking Families\n\nOur Cybersecurity Agency (@CISAgov) has lost hundreds of workers who have been furloughed. We have training for weapons of mass destruction, for detecting bombs and terrorist activities across the country, many of whom work with our local law enforcement, who have been furloughed and are not on duty today.\n\nThe Democrat Party is damaging families long-term to make a political point when it has no effect on what we are doing for immigration enforcement every single day, because that agency is funded.",
      "text_resolved": "The Democrat DHS Shutdown has Consequences for American Citizens and Hardworking Families\n\nOur Cybersecurity Agency (@CISAgov) has lost hundreds of workers who have been furloughed. We have training for weapons of mass destruction, for detecting bombs and terrorist activities across the country, many of whom work with our local law enforcement, who have been furloughed and are not on duty today.\n\nThe Democrat Party is damaging families long-term to make a political point when it has no effect on what we are doing for immigration enforcement every single day, because that agency is funded.",
