      "text": "Today, I had the privilege of joining the Western States Sheriff’s Association in Reno, NV. I am confident that increased cooperation among ICE, DHS, and local law enforcement will help accomplish what the American people voted for under President Trump — safer communities and restored law and order.\n\nWe have accomplished so much in the last year, including a 125-year low in our murder rate, and with the support of state and local law enforcement leaders, the next three years will be even better.\n\nI look forward to our continued partnership to make America safe again.",
